name: Little Does She Know 3
description:
The idea behind a lot of the work is to subvert desires, common for most of us, put them upfront, and rip them apart through the use of abstraction. AI in this case became a perfect tool to achieve the desired effect without being attached to the form, leaving only the idea of the form, thought of the form.
